Patch Set 13:

Hi Arnaud,

One of the main goals of this util is to convert version components into a long integer (64 bit value) which may be used to order a set of version data by comparing values of a single field, which may be useful when the data is persisted in DB. 
The "semantic_version" package which is present on PyPi does not have this functionality.

BTW, that package exists on pypi but is not present in global_requirements, and adding dependency their is quite long and tricky process, afaik.
